# Default: empty -> same-origin. The frontend container's nginx reverse-proxies
# /api/* and /health to host.docker.internal:5151 (the Windows backend).
# Browser stays on http://localhost:8080 so Chrome's Private Network Access
# policy doesn't block requests.
#
# Override only if you want the browser to talk to the backend directly
# (e.g. backend on a different machine). In that case the backend must also
# permit CORS (it already does for *) and Chrome's PNA must be allowed.
VITE_API_BASE=
